movie_name: The Man Who Wanted to See It All
short_description: In 1962 Heinz Stücke (20) left Germany with his bicycle and a tent. He left a life without a future, to follow a big dream: to see everything in the world. In 1996 he had been in all countries of the world. 50 years after he returns.
